items.title: Motional puts AI at center of robotaxi reboot as it targets 2026 for driverless service
items.description: Motional says it will launch a driverless robotaxi service in Las Vegas before the end of 2026.

items.title: Google co-founders may be leaving California
items.description: Sergey Brin and Larry Page appear to be pulling back from the state where they co-founded Google.

items.title: Instagram says there’s been ‘no breach’ despite password reset requests
items.description: Instagram says that although some users received suspicious-looking password reset requests, it has not been breached.

items.title: Nuclear startups are back in vogue with small reactors, and big challenges
items.description: Small modular reactor startups are betting that mass manufacturing will help them bring costs down. But are they underestimating the challenge?
